                <head>No. 1428<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>Despatch 39 from Kuwait, January 2, 1952, enclosed the English language text of a
                    decree by Sheikh Abdulla Al Salim Al Subah, the Ruler of Kuwait, imposing an
                    income tax implementing the Kuwait Oil Company’s Agreement of 1951 with the
                    Ruler of Kuwait for additional oil payments. (886D.112/1–252) For documentation
                    on the negotiation of the agreement, see <ref target="frus1951v05#pg_315">
                        <hi rend="italic">Foreign Relations</hi>, 1951, volume <hi rend="smallcaps"
                            >v</hi>, pages 315</ref> ff.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
